  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Although your first thought is to return to base camp and retrieve a lambance rig or two, you quickly realize that the space is far too large to light permanently. Instead, you need to venture forward with whatever gear you have at hand, insufficient though it may be to fully chase away the darkness or your feelings of trepidation."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As you progress steadily through the passage, you become more and more aware of the sounds made by dangers lurking within, and the odors they emit, and are thus able to avoid them without much difficulty. By relying on your full range of senses and following your instincts, you become more and more comfortable in the darkness until\u2014at last\u2014 it no longer troubles you."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Record"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "BRAVED THE DARK"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "on the campaign tracker. If you had already"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "BRAVED THE DARK"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", add up to 1"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "per_ranger",
              "color": "black"
            },
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "progress",
              "color": "black"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "to each feature in play."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
